trans-unit.source: Reorders links between nodes.
trans-unit.target: 重新排序節點之間的連結。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [list::splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[list:: splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac)。

trans-unit.source: The position in the container before which to splice.
trans-unit.target: 容器中的位置，在此位置前分離。

trans-unit.source: The container to splice from.
trans-unit.target: 要從中分離的容器。

trans-unit.source: All elements will be removed from this container after the splice operation.
trans-unit.target: 在連接 (splice) 作業之後，所有項目將會從這個容器中移除。

trans-unit.source: Inserts the given sequence into the container before the specified position.
trans-unit.target: 將指定序列插入容器的指定位置之前。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [list::splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[list:: splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac)。

trans-unit.source: The position in the container before which to splice.
trans-unit.target: 容器中的位置，在此位置前分離。

trans-unit.source: The container to splice from.
trans-unit.target: 要從中分離的容器。

trans-unit.source: The position of the element to splice.
trans-unit.target: 要連接之項目的位置。

trans-unit.source: Removes the element from the given container pointed to by <paramref name="_First" /> and inserts it before the element in the controlled sequence pointed to by <paramref name="_Where" />.
trans-unit.target: 從 <paramref name="_First" /> 所指向之指定容器移除項目，並將它插入受控制序列中 <paramref name="_Where" /> 所指向的項目之前。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [list::splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[list:: splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac)。

trans-unit.source: The position in the container before which to splice.
trans-unit.target: 容器中的位置，在此位置前分離。

trans-unit.source: The container to splice from.
trans-unit.target: 要從中分離的容器。

trans-unit.source: The beginning position of the range of elements to splice.
trans-unit.target: 要連接之項目範圍的開頭位置。

trans-unit.source: The first position beyond the range of elements to splice.
trans-unit.target: 超過要連接之項目範圍的第一個位置。

trans-unit.source: Removes the range of elements [<paramref name="_First" />, <paramref name="_Last" />) from the given container and inserts it before the element in the controlled sequence pointed to by <paramref name="_Where" />.
trans-unit.target: 從指定容器移除項目的範圍 [<paramref name="_First" />, <paramref name="_Last" />)，並將它插入至受控制序列中 <paramref name="_Where" /> 所指向的項目之前。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [list::splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[list:: splice (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/ebc424b9-8341-4a88-b101-86d56324f5ac)。

trans-unit.source: The container to swap contents with.
trans-unit.target: 要交換內容的容器。

trans-unit.source: Swaps the contents of two containers.
trans-unit.target: 交換兩個容器的內容。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [list::swap (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/188b66c2-0a08-4001-a566-41d0955c89bd).
trans-unit.target: 如需詳細資訊，請參閱[list:: swap (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/188b66c2-0a08-4001-a566-41d0955c89bd)。

trans-unit.source: The comparer that determines whether element pairs are unique.
trans-unit.target: 判斷項目組是否為唯一的比較子。

trans-unit.source: An element that is not unique will be removed from the container.
trans-unit.target: 不是唯一的項目將會從容器中移除。

trans-unit.source: Removes adjacent elements that pass a specified test.
trans-unit.target: 移除通過指定測試的相鄰項目。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [list::unique (STL/CLR)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/c3a29e4e-0ec1-4472-b050-7a9511037132).
